Challenger Mobile AB (publ) has today signed an agreement to acquire all shares in the company AB B21 Invest III, under a proposed name change to Battlecamp AB, which owns all assets and rights linked to the mobile game Battle Camp. The transaction is carried out with payment in three parts:
SEK 30 million through cash payment;
SEK 70 million through seller reverse;
SEK 80 million through shares at a price of SEK 0.06 per share.
